Package: defprit
Title: Explore Bayes Factors for Mixed Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Frederik", "Aust", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "frederik.aust@uni-koeln.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4900-788X"))
Description: Functions to run simulations on translations of prior scales from
  linear mixed models with standardized effect size parameterization to
  corresponding repeated-measures ANOVA and paired t-tests.
